# Route Target/generate to ConceptLibraryTarget — Architecture doc: Clef Bind, Sync Section 3.3

sync RouteToConceptLibrary [eager]
when {
  Target/generate: [ projection: ?p; targetType: "concept-library"; config: ?c ]
    => [ output: ?o ]
}
then {
  ConceptLibraryTarget/generate: [ config: ?c ]
}
